name: Kabeh Jati Nusa Penida Villas & Restaurant
address: Jl. Kabeh Jati Garden No. 1, Dusun Semaya, Desa Suana, Kecamatan Nusa Penida, Suana, Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1:
The triangle room is really big and comfortable, bed is amazingly big. The pool is nice and the staff were really helpful. They have restaurant opening whole day and scooter rental.
They also offer the possibility to book different activities.
Location is so far from the main beaches to see, but still a good trip with motorbike around the roads and jungle views.
review 2: Property is very nice and well equipped. We stayed in Triangle house which was very nice and spacious. Food was also very nice and tasty. People working there were very friendly and polite. This place is kids friendly.
review 3: Beautiful property, managed by a family. They're very polite, friendly and helpful. People who are looking for a great villa with excellent view can definitely come here. The sunrise is breathtaking from here.
review 4: This property is very good. Rooms are clean and location and views are awesome. Staffs are very friendly and helpful. But 2 things that kept us from giving 5 star. one is water, water that they provide was very salty. we can‚Äôt even able to bath with that water and other thing is their complementary breakfast menu which is very limited. other than that this one is very good.
review 5:
Amazing staff, great clean and new place.
The towels and lined smelled really good. Nice little view. The place on google maps lead you somewhere else but there is a road that isn‚Äôt on maps yet where you can use a motorbike or car.

The place is on the East coast of Nusa Penida so you won‚Äôt be able to see the sunset but you can see the sunrise. A little far from main attractions but good for those looking to explore the less touristic areas. Easy with motorbike.

There is good breakfast, although no big options for dinner.

name: You and We House
address: Semaya, Penida Island, Jl. Ibus, Suana, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia

The place is located far from the crowds which can be disadvantage if you don‚Äôt drive, however you can definitely rest there. Surrounded by beautiful unexplored nature, great escape from Bali to catch a breath. The rooms are clean, swimming pool with the best view. I would definitely come back, see you!
review 2:

review 3: This is a very nice and cozy hotel, there is a beautiful and clean pool and great view. But the service is average. At first our room didn‚Äôt even have soap and shampoo. It also didn‚Äôt have hair drier. The location is soo far to main points to visit. The breakfast is soo poor and for food there are just 2 options. But the staff are so friendly and nice and all the hotel were so clean. Also the rental motors in hotel were so bad and without break.
review 4: A beautiful Hostel and a nice place to stay. The rooms are clean, the personal is polite and very friendly. We enjoy our stay here very well! We like the breakfast with view to the sea! Thank you very much! ü§ó
review 5:
This is the best place to stay in Nusa Penida.
A family of 5 owns this place and everyone is so friendly and polite. They will always try their best to serve their guests. We had a stay there for almost 4 days and those were the best 4 days in Indonesia for me.
I would highly recommend this place. The rooms are very clean, classy and comfy with great room service. The view from the villas is best as you can see the infinity pool with noisy waves.

name: Horizon Nusa Penida

review 2: Rooms are small but enough. I felt like I am at home by sharing WC and kitchen actually. It‚Äôs really honestly feeling üòä and common areas are just 5stars hotel. review 3: Isolated kind of place, 40mins from Harbour, but it's good. Worth it .
review 4: We spent 2 night there and when we left we really felt like we were leaving our home. Everything was really perfect. review 5: Beautiful, clean, modern furnished homestay. The family that owns the house is very nice and welcomes you very warmly. The breakfast is delicious and the pool is also very nice and clean.
